Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:41.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{What about him?}Chuyện gì đã xảy ra với hắn?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:45.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{He got away.}Hắn thoát rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:52.36,Main,split,0,0,0,,{All our men were defeated, we ran out of\Nweapons and lost all means to—}Người của ta đều bị hạ.\NTa đã dùng mọi loại vũ khí. Ta mất tất cả—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:54.09,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Why did you come back?}Sao ngươi trở lại?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:57.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{Where is Julia?}Julia đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:01:59.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{I don't know...}Em không biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:10.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{Shin.}Shin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:13.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{Don't follow in Lin's footsteps.}Đừng đi theo vết xe đổ của Lin.
