Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{Keep going, and pass the place.}Đừng dừng lại ở phía trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:33.39,Main,split,0,0,0,,{What?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:35.21,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Someone might have gotten here already.}Có thể đã có người đến trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{Wait here.}Em đợi ở đây đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:46.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{Annie?}Annie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{I told them that you weren't here.}Tôi nói với chúng là cậu không đến đây,
