Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:00.12,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{I told them...}Tôi đã nói như thế, nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:01.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Don't talk.}Đừng nói nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:06.12,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Vicious killed off the elders, they said.}Chúng nói... Vicious đã giết các trưởng lão. 
