Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:06.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{Where's Vicious? [extra lead-in}Vicious đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:09.36,Main,split,0,0,0,,{On the top floor. This way.}Trên tầng thượng. Lối này.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:25.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{Shin!}Shin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{Shin!}Shin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:36.47,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{Please defeat... Vicious...}Hãy đánh bại... Vicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{Actually...}Sự thật là...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{I wanted you to come back...}tôi đã rất muốn anh quay lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:15.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{So, you are finally awake.}Cuối cùng anh cũng đã tỉnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{I told you before, Spike}Tôi đã nói rồi mà, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:22.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{that I am the only one who can kill you.}Tôi là người duy nhất có thể giết anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:25.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'll return those words back to you, Vicious.}Cũng chỉ có tôi\Nmới giết được anh, Vicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:28.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{Either way, we were\Ndestined to end up like this.}Ta đã được định trước có kết cục thế này.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:17:59.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{Julia passed away.}Julia chết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:04.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{Let's end it all.}Kết thúc chuyện này đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:05.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{If that's your wish.}Tôi sẽ cho anh toại nguyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:34.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{This is...}Tất cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{a dream...}chỉ là giấc mơ phải không anh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:39.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{Just a bad dream...}Chỉ là cơn ác mộng thôi em.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:10.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{Bang...}Bùm!
Dialogue: 1,0:24:03.03,0:24:08.20,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,{\an8}NỖI NIỀM ĐÓ SẼ MÃI THEO TA.
